page.title: 03Mikaler's Diary part 2.
page.content: When I got home from school I tidied up the lounge before my mum came home from work.Then I watched{"Kids from {Degrassi Street"}and{"Who Sir? Me Sir" on{BBC Television.}When my mum came in she started the tea so I went upstairs and played some tapes.For my tea I had {cod, parsley sauce}and{oven chips. Then we had{peaches}and{Nestles {cream.}After tea I started washing up but half way through I watched the end of{"Emmerdale Farm"}on television again. Later I telephoned my friend Lisa and she came to play at my house.I helped my mum put the ironing away and I went to bed at{10.00pm.
